**where —** Arrakis — the desert planet, and five thousand years of the human future  Framework inputs: the spice melange; prescience; the Bene Gesserit; the Golden Path  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0 · Universe David 0)

**why —** He who controls the spice controls the universe; and prescience is a trap.

**how —** Crystallized from the main corpus — the six novels of Frank Herbert.

**◌ the mythos —** He who controls the spice controls the universe; and prescience is a trap. Dune won the Hugo and the first-ever Nebula, and is the best-selling science-fiction novel of all time.

